{"tid":2478543,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"何雁詩自責令老公被指「食軟飯」：咁啱每次我埋單都畀記者影到！","createTime":"2021-04-07T06:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T07:22:55.000Z","uid":212249,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6dc337db9986bc685c0b1d167ca7601051ae64d2","tid":2478543,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.presslogic.com/holiday.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/a69775ba.jpg?auto=format&amp;w=830&amp;q=100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.presslogic.com%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F04%2Fa69775ba.jpg%3Fauto%3Dformat%26w%3D830%26q%3D100&h=21c97f78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTVB《解構心機女》除咗有馮盈盈江嘉敏，仲有人妻何雁詩。佢於新一集提到過往嘅「慘痛經歷」，令同佢一齊食飯嘅男仔都被人指係「食軟飯」！<br />\n<br />\n《解構心機女》最大話題除咗有馮盈盈同江嘉敏充滿火花嘅互動之外，新一集仲請咗何雁詩同朱敏瀚做嘉賓，兩人都喺節目中分享同另一半嘅相處點滴。<br />\n<br />\n何雁詩提到每次問老公鄭俊弘「我今日有咩唔同」，對方都答唔出：「明明朝早同佢講我去整睫毛，夜晚問佢『我有咩唔同咗？』，佢淨係會話：『變靚咗！』」，不過何雁詩就話佢接受呢個答案。<br />\n<br />\n到情景題環節，被問到當差唔多食完飯會唔會主動埋單，全場只有何雁詩舉交叉牌，佢以自己之前經歷解釋指都曾經試過AA制或者主動請客，但點知被人多次影到係佢埋單，於是個男仔就被寫成「食軟飯」。<br />\n<br />\n何雁詩講到相當無奈，馮盈盈即拍佢膊頭表示同情，何雁詩指上網買餸自己畀錢或私底下同返對方拆帳都無所謂，但喺外面一定要畀男仔埋單。<br />\n<br />\n早前何雁詩同鄭俊弘慶祝拍拖4周年，佢甜蜜表示由佢負責book枱，老公埋單，又指老公以前試過送百合同菊花畀佢，婚後肯為佢改變，轉送黃玫瑰令佢非常感動！"},{"pid":"49bfce70566072218a339f57d64aed3263e91f98","tid":2478543,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:41:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/233982/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholiday.presslogic.com%2Farticle%2F233982%2F&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtLQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=21050c64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://holiday.presslogic.com/article/233982/</a>"},{"pid":"90fa9b4d6cea26881b2168ab69698c38fe4c4835","tid":2478543,"uid":217641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:41:10.000Z","msg":"食軟飯犯法呀"},{"pid":"0b6fdc037224024b76d2a34a25c18ec3322c77d0","tid":2478543,"uid":76804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"吳家樂: am i a joke to you?"},{"pid":"d59a15697252788ca11274c42a2357610c1c7e29","tid":2478543,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:42:36.000Z","msg":"都係客觀事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4817edc444a29e5b21d8b6a8403600e9f1516e","tid":2478543,"uid":34517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:44:15.000Z","msg":"奸夫淫婦快啲仆街死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39409c1e1afe9dffa8e8c67e68cc8e90b228626","tid":2478543,"uid":339630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T06:46:55.000Z","msg":"人地兩公婆點相處關你鬼事咩"},{"pid":"69674865e1bc6d15dfd0d31b10210b5d60d4ac70","tid":2478543,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:04:55.000Z","msg":"出張附屬卡比老公咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03353fa0f5d4e17b8d2925909171046f045651d8","tid":2478543,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:16:14.000Z","msg":"有6億身家的小坂めぐる<br />\n好想做駙馬爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fd2f98eb034997d3e7244d097bf33725aa4290b","tid":2478543,"uid":229436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:16:56.000Z","msg":"邊個有錢咪養邊個 有咩所謂 <br />\n依家連性都變得的時代<br />\n性別都唔太重要"},{"pid":"65d9d54346919c23af656f50d48ca57ea11df34b","tid":2478543,"uid":334957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T07:17:45.000Z","msg":"好心何生下次自己俾錢啦"},{"pid":"315fc645f230524a1a661f7193eeffbce2120674","tid":2478543